| SA-4 Acquisition Process (infrastructure) | Common — AWS | AWS acquires and validates infrastructure components through supply chain security processes documented in FedRAMP authorization | Review FedRAMP package where available; rely on AWS SOC 2 for supply chain security of managed services |

