**Boundary Protection — SC-7**

| Control | AWS Portion | MyClinic Portion |
|---|---|---|
| SC-7 Boundary Protection | AWS provides VPC with configurable security groups; AWS provides WAF capability; AWS provides Network ACL capability | MyClinic must configure security groups with least-privilege rules; MyClinic must configure and maintain WAF rules including OWASP ruleset; MyClinic must define Network ACL rules; MyClinic must configure VPC routing to restrict traffic flows |

